                <span class="dropt">
                <%=image_tag('warnings/003.png', :id => "003png", class: 'warning', title: "Brake System Alert - this light indicates a low brake fluid level and professional help should be sought to rectify any issues, leaks or low brake linings are a common cause, this light is sometimes used when a vehicle has an ABS fault.", :onclick=>"populateData('input047','Brake System Light','input047close');".html_safe)%>
